{"id":25649,"type":6,"name":"极楽町一丁目 嫁姑地狱篇","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c8/0b/25649_5X65K.jpg","rating":{"total":2,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6},"summary":"清静的住宅区，极乐町一处日本房屋内，儿媳“のりこ”照顾着病弱的婆婆“とみ”。\r\n丈夫由于外派至国外，故只有婆媳二人。\r\n宛如小津安二郎的电影一样，“のりこ”和“とみ”之间呈现着安静生活的本来面貌。\r\n在这样的生活中，“のりこ”无意间露出的一句长吁短叹：「就像死了那样累啊…」。\r\n于是瞬间，餐室变为战场！小津安二郎变为「黑客帝国」！\r\n这是部纯日本式的功夫片，在好莱坞没有，在香港也没有。\r\n曾获日本漫画家协会奖的喜剧「极乐町一丁目　婆媳地狱篇」(二阶堂正宏/朝日新闻社刊)，将以在线武打和CG满载的娱乐形式用每集5分钟的时间勾勒刻画出来。\r\n日本的婆媳问题就此解决！","info":"<li><span>集数: </span>12</li><li><span>开始: </span>2008</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>每集长: </span>5分钟</li><li><span>电视台: </span>WOWOW</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.wowow.co.jp/drama/gokuraku/</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":2},"eps":[{"id":129284,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129284","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129285,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129285","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129286,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129286","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129287,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129287","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129288,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129288","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129289,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129289","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129290,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129290","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":129291,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/129291","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":12